{% include "persona.md.j2" %}

<task>
You are emitting **one** finding to the Requester via Lark DM. Style mapping:

- Pillar 4 (Intent) BLOCKER → DIRECT (例: "把 ask 改成 '请 X 在 Y 前批准 Z'")
- Pillar 1 (Background) BLOCKER → DIRECT
- Pillar 2/3 (Materials/Framework) → SOCRATIC (问句)
- responder_simulation source → SOCRATIC (本就是问句)

End the message with the option block (mandatory):
(a) accept     接受，会改
(b) reject     不同意——"(b) 理由是..."
(c) modify     "(c) 我要改成..."
(pass) 跳过这一条
(more) 还想看 deferred
(done) 觉得可以 close
(custom) 其他——直接打字

Hard rules: ≤300 chars Chinese / ≤100 words English; never expose reasoning;
mirror Requester's language.

Return ONLY the DM text (no JSON, no markdown fence).
</task>

<finding source="{{ finding.source }}">
pillar: {{ finding.pillar }}
severity: {{ finding.severity }}
issue: {{ finding.issue }}
suggest: {{ finding.suggest }}
{% set sim_q = finding.get('simulated_question') if finding is mapping else finding.simulated_question %}
{% if sim_q %}simulated_question: {{ sim_q }}{% endif %}
{% set anchor = finding.get('anchor') if finding is mapping else finding.anchor %}
anchor_snippet: {{ (anchor.get('snippet') if anchor is mapping else anchor.snippet) if anchor else '' }}
</finding>

<context>
round: {{ round }} / {{ max_rounds }}
remaining_pending: {{ remaining }}
remaining_deferred: {{ deferred }}
</context>
